<plot>With Christmas you try and want to be with your family or loved ones. For snowmen that isn't different. Just in time a lonesome snowman trucker finds out it's the 25th of December. He hops to his truck and starts the long, long way home. While around him Christmas lights pop up everywhere, miles of road are still ahead. Is there time enough to surprise his waiting wife?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?411314</url></doc>
